---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../../components/Footer.astro';

const title = "Atermicos Pinamar - Caso de Éxito | Algoritmia";
const description = "Expansión geográfica y generación de leads High-Ticket mediante publicidad digital.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <Header />
  
  <main class="bg-white text-black selection:bg-cyan-100">
    <section class="relative pt-32 pb-20 px-6 md:px-12 overflow-hidden">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto relative z-10">
        <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-12 items-center">
          <div class="flex-1 space-y-8">
            <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 rounded-full border border-gray-200 bg-gray-50">
              <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-cyan-500"></span>
              <span class="text-xs font-medium text-gray-600 uppercase tracking-wide">Logística & Publicidad</span>
            </div>
            
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight leading-tight text-black mb-8">
              Expansión geográfica y <span class="text-gray-500">aumento de pedidos con envíos.</span>
            </h1>
            
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-500 max-w-xl leading-relaxed mb-8">
              Sin página web y dependiendo del "boca a boca", implementamos un sistema de publicidad directa que genera entre 5 y 10 oportunidades de venta diarias.
            </p>

            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-6 items-start md:items-center">
              <a href="https://instagram.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-3 rounded-full bg-black text-white font-medium hover:bg-gray-800 transition-colors">
                Ver Instagram
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">arrow_outward</span>
              </a>

              <div class="flex items-center gap-3 px-4 py-2 rounded-full bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100">
                <span class="text-cyan-600 font-bold">5-10</span>
                <span class="text-sm text-gray-600 font-medium">Leads Diarios</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="flex-1 w-full">
            <div class="relative aspect-[4/3] rounded-3xl overflow-hidden border border-gray-100 bg-gray-50 shadow-2xl shadow-gray-200/50 group">
              <img 
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1562778612-e1e0cda9915c?q=80&w=2070&auto=format&fit=crop" 
                alt="Atermicos Pinamar Obra" 
                class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-700 group-hover:scale-105"
              />
              <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/10 to-transparent"></div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 px-6 md:px-12 bg-gray-50 relative">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center space-y-8">
        <blockquote class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-medium text-black leading-tight max-w-5xl mx-auto">
          "Fabricamos bordes de piscina de alta calidad, pero vendemos poco online. Queremos duplicar las ventas en 6 meses, aprovechando la temporada alta."
        </blockquote>
        <p class="text-gray-400 mt-6 font-medium">— El Desafío & Expectativa</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-32 px-6 md:px-12 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="text-center mb-20">
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-6 text-black">Hoja de Ruta: 6 Meses</h2>
          <p class="text-gray-500 text-lg">Estrategia intensiva de captación de clientes sin necesidad de sitio web complejo.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
          <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 hover:border-gray-300 transition-colors group relative overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 text-xs font-bold text-green-600 bg-green-100 px-2 py-1 rounded-full">Completado</div>
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border border-gray-200 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-black">foundation</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-3">Mes 1: Bases</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Optimización del catálogo digital y configuración de pixel de seguimiento para medir conversiones.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-cyan-50 border border-cyan-200 hover:border-cyan-300 transition-colors group relative overflow-hidden ring-2 ring-cyan-500 ring-offset-2">
             <div class="absolute top-4 right-4 text-xs font-bold text-cyan-600 bg-cyan-100 px-2 py-1 rounded-full animate-pulse">Actual</div>
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border border-cyan-100 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-cyan-600">ads_click</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-3">Mes 2: Tracción</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Lanzamiento de campañas en Google Ads (Búsqueda) y Meta Ads (Retargeting) para captar demanda activa.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 hover:border-gray-300 transition-colors group">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border border-gray-200 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-black">trending_up</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-3">Mes 3-4: Escalamiento</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Aumento de presupuesto en las campañas ganadoras y expansión de la publicidad a nuevas zonas geográficas.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="p-8 rounded-3xl bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 hover:border-gray-300 transition-colors group">
            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mb-6 border border-gray-200 group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform">
              <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-black">handshake</span>
            </div>
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black mb-3">Mes 5-6: Consolidación</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
              Estrategia B2B de fidelización para constructores y arquitectos para asegurar flujo constante fuera de temporada.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-32 px-6 md:px-12 bg-gray-50">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <div class="inline-block px-3 py-1 rounded-lg bg-cyan-100 text-cyan-700 text-sm font-bold mb-2">
                Resultados Parciales (Mes 2)
            </div>
            <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-black">El Cambio Real</h2>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-lg">
              Al activar las campañas, pasaron de depender del "boca a boca" a asegurar la temporada con consultas de alto valor.
            </p>
            
            <div class="space-y-6">
              <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-gray-200 shadow-sm">
                <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 uppercase mb-2 tracking-wider">Situación Inicial</p>
                <div class="flex items-end gap-4">
                  <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-400">Sin Publicidad</span>
                  <span class="text-sm text-gray-400 mb-1">(Venta Pasiva)</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="p-6 rounded-2xl bg-white border border-cyan-500 shadow-lg">
                <p class="text-xs text-cyan-600 uppercase mb-2 font-bold tracking-wider">Resultado Actual</p>
                <div class="flex items-end gap-4">
                  <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-black">5-10 Leads/día</span>
                </div>
                <p class="text-gray-600 font-medium mt-2 text-sm flex items-center gap-1">
                  <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px] text-cyan-500">check_circle</span>
                  Proyectos High-Ticket (Piscinas)
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="pt-4">
              <p class="text-5xl font-bold text-black tracking-tighter">
                Temporada
              </p>
              <p class="text-gray-500 mt-2 text-xl font-medium">Asegurada con obras cerradas</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="relative h-[400px] bg-white rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 shadow-xl shadow-gray-200/50 p-8 flex flex-col justify-end overflow-hidden">
            <div class="absolute top-8 left-8">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-black">Generación de Demanda</h3>
              <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm">Consultas Diarias Promedio</p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex items-end justify-center gap-12 h-[200px] w-full px-8">
              <div class="w-24 bg-gray-100 rounded-t-lg h-[10%] relative group flex justify-center">
                 <div class="absolute -top-8 text-xs font-bold text-gray-400">0-1</div>
                 <div class="absolute -bottom-8 text-sm text-gray-500 font-medium">Orgánico</div>
              </div>
              
              <div class="w-24 bg-cyan-500 rounded-t-lg h-[90%] relative group flex justify-center shadow-lg shadow-cyan-200">
                 <div class="absolute -top-8 text-xl font-bold text-black">10+</div>
                 <div class="absolute -bottom-8 text-sm text-black font-bold">Con Ads</div>
                 
                 <div class="absolute top-4 w-full border-t border-white/30"></div>
                 <div class="absolute top-8 w-full border-t border-white/30"></div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="w-full h-px bg-gray-200 mt-10"></div>
             <p class="text-center text-xs text-gray-400 mt-4">Comparativa Mes 0 vs Mes 2</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="py-24 text-center bg-black text-white">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6">
        <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">¿Tu negocio necesita vender más?</h2>
        <p class="text-white/60 text-lg mb-10">
          Creamos sistemas de ventas predecibles, incluso si no tienes sitio web.
        </p>
        <a href="/#contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-white text-black px-6 py-3 rounded-full font-medium text-sm hover:bg-gray-200 transition-colors shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl">
          Solicitar Presupuesto
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[18px]">arrow_forward</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</Layout>